SVC â€“ Service Handling
======================

A simple service manager written in shell.
Only handles starting and stopping services, no monitoring, no logging.

Installation
------------

	$ make install

Creating service scripts
------------------------

	$ touch /etc/svc.d/avail/<service>
	$ $EDITOR /etc/svc.d/avail/<service>
	$ svc -s <service>

There are some example scripts in examples/ dir

Usage
-----

See the manpage or help function for available documentation

Have fun!
